Preheat oven to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C). Beat together the cream cheese and the SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener, add the pumpkin and the spices. Beat in egg whites one at a time. Add salt. Beat until creamy. Pour the batter evenly into the two pastry shells. Bake at 350 degrees F (175 degrees C) for 50 minutes or until a knife inserted in the center comes out clean. Let cool then top with whipped topping.